<h1>Routing</h1>
<p class="lead">Define how your application responds to client requests in <code>config/routes.soli</code>.</p>

<h2>Basic Routes</h2>
<p>Map HTTP verbs to controller actions:</p>

<pre><code class="language-soli">get("/about", "home#about");
post("/users", "users#create");
put("/users/:id", "users#update");
delete("/users/:id", "users#delete");</code></pre>

<h2>Resource Routing</h2>
<p>Automatically generate standard RESTful routes for a resource:</p>

<pre><code class="language-soli">resources("photos", null);</code></pre>

<p>This creates paths like <code>/photos</code>, <code>/photos/new</code>, <code>/photos/:id</code>, etc.</p>

<h2>Scoped Middleware</h2>
<p>Apply middleware to specific groups of routes:</p>

<pre><code class="language-soli">middleware("auth", -> {
    get("/dashboard", "dashboard#index");
    resources("settings", null);
});</code></pre>
